            <spirit:description> rf_write_ongoing, this is a status register for write through mode to avoid potential coherence issue.\n1’b1: the cache is still doing AHB write transaction to the main memory and the data is not written into the main memory.\n1’b0: the cache has finished AHB write transaction and the data is written into the main memory. </spirit:description>
            <spirit:bitOffset>7</spirit:bitOffset>
